Package: datavalr
Title: Tools for Data Validation and Quality Assessment
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Oscar", "Mercado", , "oscarmercado@college.harvard.edu", role = "cre")
Description: 
  The datavalr package provides tools for validating and assessing the quality of datasets. 
  It includes functions to diagnose empty values, summarize column attributes, track outliers, 
  validate betting metrics, and ensure chronological order in time-series data. These functions 
  are designed to facilitate data cleaning, quality control, and exploratory data analysis.
